column5: Hi Guys..Going fishing with Rick tonight. I guess I'll have to show him how it's done...LOL!
Oh please do Jewel!!! I want you should whip him real good!!!  Take the camera for evidence!
sigh... I am so putting her on Mod Q I am bringing the camera.. we shall see what happens.
I want to see all pics.
Hey Rick!... don't forget the Egyptian Princess and Tammy Faye Baker Jumla's!!!
Okay...I got schooled! Pics and report coming!! You will not believe what she caught...now I know how Cliff feels fishing with Bly.
Get used to it.  Thank god my honey fears the fish!
Read Rick's report this morning Jewel...way to call that one! LOL   At least you have proof if you say "I told ya so"!  Congrates again on the beauty walleye!
